      "author": "PandoraReads",
      "description": "## v1.1.1 Release Notes\n\n### AI Prompt Selection Modal\n- Click \"Full-text AI Analysis\" or card \"AI Research\" button now opens a prompt selection modal\n- Users can choose from preset research prompts before sending to the AI model for analysis\n\n### Quick Commands\n- Added sync-related quick commands, accessible via Command Palette (Cmd/Ctrl+P):\n  - Export sync data to vault\n  - Import sync data from vault\n\n### Installation\n1. Download `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css`\n2. Place them in `.obsidian/plugins/hilighter/` directory\n3. Enable the plugin in Obsidian Settings",
